Michel Vuillermoz https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michel_Vuillermoz 0 Michel Vuillermoz (born 18 December 1962) is a French actor and scriptwriter. Vuillermoz has appeared in more than 100 films and 40 plays. In 1998, he received two Molière Award: Best Male Newcomer and Best Play for André le Magnifique. Since 2007, he is one of the Sociétaires of the Comédie-Française. Michel_Vuillermoz ( born_18_December_1962 ) is a_French_actor_and_scriptwriter .
